OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,FA former Merthyr Tydfil care home has
OL,7,Fbeen transformed to help house
OL,8,Fhomeless people in the area.
OL,10,FMarsh House in Merthyr Tydfil was
OL,11,Fpreviously the Glan-yr-Afon Care Home
OL,12,Fand the building's refurbishment has
OL,13,Fbeen supported by the Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment's Transforming Towns
OL,15,FCapital Funding and core capital
OL,16,Ffunding from Merthyr Tydfil County
OL,17,FBorough Council (MTCBC).
OL,19,FFor one resident, Marsh House has
OL,20,F"turned his life around."
