OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,FSimon Sharpe says he became homeless
OL,7,Fafter a relationship breakdown and
OL,8,Fstruggled to find somewhere to live.
OL,9,FHe ended up living in his car for
OL,10,Faround four months.
OL,12,FThe council then sent him to the a
OL,13,Fhotel where he stayed for eight months.
OL,15,F"The people were nice, it's just there
OL,16,Fwere certain aspects of the hotel - it
OL,17,Fhad a reputation," Simon said of his
OL,18,Fexperience there.
OL,20,FHe was then selected to come to Marsh
OL,21,FHouse.
