OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"This place has turned my life around
OL,7,F- it's absolutely fantastic here," he
OL,8,Fsaid
OL,10,F"My mental health was hit really
OL,11,Fbadly," he added. "I didn't know what
OL,12,FI was doing every day. I wasn't
OL,13,Fsleeping at all, I was awake for days.
OL,14,FIt was a struggle. But the first two
OL,15,Fnights I came here, I slept like a
OL,16,Fbaby."
OL,18,FAt Marsh House, Simon has meetings
OL,19,Fwith support workers to talk about how
OL,20,Fhe's doing, which he says has helped
OL,21,Fwith his mental health.
