OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"The support staff help you in any way
OL,7,Fthat you need, which is really good
OL,8,Fbecause you don't have that every
OL,9,Fwhere else, even in standard life," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"I feel normal - I haven't for a
OL,13,Fwhile. I feel like myself again."
OL,15,FSimon works as a photographer but says
OL,16,Fit's not a job that brings in a weekly
OL,17,Fwage. However, after speaking to
OL,18,Fsupport staff, Simon has been inspired
OL,19,Fto look into becoming a support worker
OL,20,Fhimself and is pursuing a course to
OL,21,Fhelp him get a job in the area.
