OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"My struggle has made me realise what
OL,7,FI want to go on and do," he said.
OL,9,FSimon now feels at a point where he
OL,10,Fknows what he wants to do it life.
OL,11,F"I'm slowly getting there - it's
OL,12,Fnice," he said.
OL,14,FThe project has been developed in
OL,15,Fpartnership with MTCBC, the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment, Merthyr Valleys Homes, and
OL,17,FPobl housing association.
