OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,FIt will become a homelessness
OL,7,Fassessment and triage centre with
OL,8,Fshort, sharp interventions for those
OL,9,Frequiring temporary accommodation in a
OL,10,Fcrisis. The building combines living
OL,11,Fspace and support services.
OL,13,FLorraine Griffiths is an Assistant
OL,14,FDirector with Pobl.
OL,16,F"This particularly is close to my
OL,17,Fheart because I'm from Merthyr - this
OL,18,Fis my home," she said.
