OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"It's been vital - to live in a hotel
OL,7,Fas long as these individuals have is
OL,8,Fsoul-destroying. Somewhere like this
OL,9,Fis somewhere where they can start to
OL,10,Ffeel back to normal, somewhere they
OL,11,Fcan call home, somewhere they can
OL,12,Fcook, do their washing, without living
OL,13,Fin one room," she added.
OL,15,FCabinet Secretary for Housing, Local
OL,16,FGovernment, and Planning, Julie James,
OL,17,Falso paid a visit to Marsh House.
