OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"The longer somebody is homeless, the
OL,7,Fmore cost to the system there is but
OL,8,Fthe much more human cost there is too.
OL,9,FFor both reasons, this is an excellent
OL,10,Fexample of where we want to go and,
OL,11,Fyes, we're looking to build more of
OL,12,Fthese across Wales," she said.
OL,14,FCommenting, Mark Isherwood MS, Shadow
OL,15,FHousing Minister, said:
