OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"Whilst it is the right thing to find
OL,7,Femergency accommodation for people who
OL,8,Fdesperately need it, more needs to be
OL,9,Fdone to treat the cause of
OL,10,Fhomelessness in Wales, not just the
OL,11,Fsymptoms.
OL,13,FThe causes of homelessness are usually
OL,14,Fcomplex and short sharp interventions
OL,15,Fwithout person-centred support risk
OL,16,Ftrapping people in a "revolving door"
OL,17,Fcycle.
