OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"Labour's record on homelessness in
OL,7,FWales is shocking and unless they make
OL,8,Fdrastic wholesale changes, this
OL,9,Fproblem will only get worse."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Plaid Cymru said:
OL,12,F"Plaid Cymru supports efforts to
OL,13,Fprevent, reduce, and ultimately end
OL,14,Fhomelessness in Wales.
OL,16,F"We recognise that access to secure
OL,17,Fhousing and accommodation plays an
OL,18,Fimportant role in that goal.
