OL,3,C'It's turned my life around': Former
OL,4,Ccare home being used for the homeless
OL,6,F"That's why we have proposed a Right
OL,7,Fto Adequate Housing Act in Wales,
OL,8,Fwhich would include powers to
OL,9,Fintroduce rent controls and other
OL,10,Fmarket interventions to make housing
OL,11,Fmore affordable and help ensure each
OL,12,Fperson in Wales has access to secure
OL,13,Faccommodation."
